data.description: Welcome to the beautiful neighborhood of Culpepper Landing!  This vibrant community is known for its social events, including monthly gatherings that bring neighbors together. With a golf cart-friendly environment, you can easily explore the neighborhood and nearby amenities which include an outdoor pool/waterpark, clubhouse, fitness center, trails and access to the Intracoastal Waterway.  This home has been freshly painted throughout and offers a 2 car garage for convenient parking and extra storage. 3 large bedrooms 2.5 baths plus a spacious Loft. The beautiful Dining Room & Great Room flows into the Eat-in Kitchen with upgraded cabinets, granite counters and stainless appliances.  Additional Morning Room off kitchen. This home offers an open and flowing floorplan!  Lots of curb appeal and landscaping. Trex decking with vinyl railings for easy maintenance. Step outside to a beautiful fenced backyard ideal for outdoor cooking, recreation and relaxation!
